### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:8000/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "middleName": null,
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "alice.smith@example.com",
  "addresses": [
    {
      "type": "home",
      "street1": "123 Main St",
      "city": "Springfield",
      "state": "IL",
      "postalCode": "62704",
      "country": "US"
    }
  ],
  "phoneNumbers": [
    {
      "type": "mobile",
      "countryCode": "+1",
      "number": "555-1234"
    }
  ],
  "notificationPreferences": {
    "email": true,
    "sms": false,
    "push": true,
    "mail": false
  }
}

###

### List all customers
GET http://localhost:8000/customers

###

### Get a single customer by ID
# (replace {{id}} with the actual ID returned above)
GET http://localhost:8000/customers/468a582c-128a-46f2-b1a8-fd5876fba844

###

### Update a customer (partial)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/customers/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.new@example.com"
}

###

### Delete a customer
DELETE http://localhost:8000/customers/{{id}}
